        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <img class="img-circle" src="/assets/exam.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
          <h2>Exam</h2>
          <p>Quiz-Creator has been a great tool to create online training for hundreds of employees in the world. Quiz-Creator has allowed us to provide over 3,000 sessions, anytime & anywhere.</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/users/sign_in" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <img class="img-circle" src="/assets/test.png" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
          <h2>Test</h2>
          <p>Makes training & testing super easy. You only create test , assign student to group. Quizzes are fun! Give your users a chance to play with their knowledge</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/users/sign_in" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <img class="img-circle" src="/assets/result.png" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
