        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7">
          <%= image_tag "create-online-quiz", class: "featurette-image img-responsive center-block" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading">And lastly, we can see a result. <span class="text-muted">Check now.</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">Allow students to see a feedback of the questions they got right and wrong.Sign up for a free account and give it a whirl </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <%= image_tag "integrate-quiz-exam-api", class: "featurette-image img-responsive center-block" %>
